def get_note(pitch):
    pitch_ref = 440
    note_ref = "A"
    notes = {
        440: "A",
        466.16: "A#",
        493.88: "B",
        523.25: "C",
        554.37: "C#",
        587.33: "D",
        622.25: "D#",
        659.25: "E",
        698.46: "F",
        739.99: "F#",
        830.61: "G#"
    }
    for ref_pitch, ref_note in notes.items():
        if pitch % ref_pitch == 0 or pitch % (ref_pitch * 2) == 0:
            multiplier = pitch / ref_pitch
            exponent = 0
            while multiplier != 1 and multiplier != 2:
                multiplier /= 2
                exponent += 1
            if exponent % 12 == 0:
                return ref_note
            else:
                note_position = list(notes.values()).index(ref_note) + exponent % 12
                return list(notes.values())[note_position % 12]
    return "Note not found"
